People down here don't really get the appeal of NTR. It's all about shame and humiliation which is a pretty common theme among hentai works whether it's NTR or not. You really get to dive into the mindset of a character and feel all that, watching them either continuously regret it, or willingly enjoy it through a transition. At that point, they've become scum according to a common standard. Usually guys would want to humiliate someone like that to gain some sort of vengeful satisfaction. This the role the agressor tries to fill in despite being the cause of the conflict. They kind of test the victims sense of loyalty. If the girl remains loyal she'll gain sympathy, respect, and shame, forming a connection with the reader and they might show appreciation through a big large coom. If the girl is disloyal, she'll gain disgust, anger, humiliation (say it with me) *shame*. It's all about shame.
